Summary: Objects came out of a canyon and then climbed
divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking out the window towards the mountains, the first object came out of the canyon and it seemed to be a helicopter, I'm not sure what it was though because it was dark. After that object climbed away from the canyon two more objects came from the same place the first one did. A total of 6 objects were sighted coming out of the canyon. I really am not sure what it was, if it were a helicopter it would've had to of been military. As the objects went to the north they just disappear, no more lights. I just thought it was pretty weird. I saw something way different about two weeks ago and now that I found this website I will have to post it.
